pages-strings.Loom Network allows developers to build: Loom Network allows developers to build large-scale games and social apps by using DAppChains — DApps running as their own sidechains. More specifically, a DAppChain is an Application Specific Sidechain, that runs parallel to a mainchain, Ethereum in this case.

We will have updated source samples soon with a fullgame built on a DAppchain. Developers will be able to send and recieve transactions on a blockchain, including with a websocket realtime api.
